  "description": [
    "OMAHA CHAMBER of COMMERCE Amalia will entertain Nebraska Uni cameral legislators state administrative officials and judiciary representatives and their wives on Tuesday March 12 at the Chamber of Commerce The oc casion will be the traditional Legislat ive reception and dinner given by the Chamber and Omaha businessmen J he event held every two years while the Unicameral is in session will be in the Chambers main dining room The state guests will come to Omaha by special chartered busses The recep tion will begin at 5 30 p m with the dinner program scheduled to begin at 630 p m Chamber President M Cooper Smith in announcing the affair en couraged Omahan to attend adding this is of great importance to Omaha and its businessmen Thereception and dinner help immeasurably in creating a better understanding of mutual pro blems and also assist in becoming better acquainted with our state representat ives The event is of special significance this year because of the large number of legislative bills introduced for Uni cameral action in the current session Mr Smith added Nebraska Governor Victor Ander son Speaker of the Legislature John E Beaver and Nebraska Supreme Court Justice Robert Simmons and"
